苑等的居民提供服務。本站的整體設計及建造，均以融合鄰近的民居及環境爲主題。例如：提供充足的行人及行車通道從車站接駁到鄰近的屋苑等。於建築期間，減低對居民的影響，也是一個重要的議題。所以，在建築期間，特別建造了一條臨時行人天橋橫跨整個工地，爲居民提供方便的來往通道。由於西鐵的通車，美孚站及其天台上的空中花園落成啓用，鄰近一帶地區的交通及環境得以大幅改善，居民的生活質素也相應提高。</p><br/><br/>',17.00),(102,'iaiy4dpdr4g1wot4fjzmfflh','Mei Foo Station (KCRC West Rail Project Contract No. CC-404)','2025-06-02 06:55:26.761000','2025-07-07 07:13:55.837000',NULL,8,36,'en','Mei Foo Station','Kowloon Canton Railway Corporation','02 August 1999 - 31 October 2003','<p>The Mei Foo Station is situated inside the Mei Foo Park. It adopts a fully enclosed design. The unique feature of the design is to achieve a complete integration with the Lai Chi Kok Park. The roof of the station landscaped with plants, features an innovative rooftop parkland together with play equipment and facilities for the public particularly for the densely populated adjacent estates like the Mei Foo Sun Chuen and the Ching Lai Garden. The complete integration with the surrounding environment is the main feature for both the design and construction of the station, for example: provision of sufficient footpaths and vehicular link roads between the station and the adjacent housing estates. Minimizing the impact to the adjacent residents during the construction stage was also a major concern. A temporary footbridge running across the site was constructed so as to provide convenient passage for the pedestrian. With the commencement of the operation of the West Rail and the completion and opening of the rooftop parkland at the roof of the Mei Foo station, the transportation and the environment of the surrounding area was substantially improved.The quality of living for thelocal residents was also enhanced.</p>',17.00),(105,'gk6avtsh9w9qe4005il99j3l','美孚站 (九广铁路 西铁合约编号CC-404)','2025-06-02 06:56:30.847000','2025-07-07 07:13:59.653000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','美孚站','九广铁路公司','1999 年 08 月 02 日 - 2003 年 10 月 31 日','<p>美孚站位于荔枝角公园内，采用密封式设计。其设计特色在于使车站与公园环境融为一体。车站的天台设计为空中花园，其中包括园林绿化及各种休闲设施，为邻近的大型高密度住宅区如美孚新村及清丽苑等的居民提供服务。本站的整体设计及建造，均以融入相邻居民区与环境为主题。例如：提供足够的人行道及车道从车站通往邻近的住宅区等。在建筑期间减低对居民的影响，也是一个重要的事项。所以，在建筑期间，专门修建了一条临时人行天桥横跨整个工地，为居民提供方便的来往通道。工程完成后，由于西铁的通车，美孚站及其天台上的空中花园的建成启用，大幅改善了邻近地区的交通及环境，居民的生活质素也得到相应提高。</p>',17.00),(107,'zknnjhjgk8b4hj3x6dcbkbq0','內河碼頭辦公室及貨倉大樓','2025-06-02 06:58:03.571000','2025-07-07 07:14:01.775000',NULL,8,36,'zh-Hant-HK','內河碼頭辦公室及貨倉大樓','屯門內河碼頭公司','1997 年 03 月 01 日 - 1998 年 08 月 01 日','<p>工程的主要內容包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造承扥大樓的樁柱及地基</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造大樓之樓房結構</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造貯油缸及液體燃料貯存設施</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>設計，供應及安裝卷閘</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>樓房機電工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>樓房裝修工程</li></ul>',18.00),(109,'wtqh6e1lrk7uf89fik28mj5u','内河码头办公室及货仓大楼','2025-06-02 06:58:41.417000','2025-07-07 07:14:00.709000',NULL,8,36,'zh-CN','内河码头办公室及货仓大楼','屯门内河码头公司','1997 年 03 月 01 日 - 1998 年 08 月 01 日','<p>工程的主要内容包括：</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造承扥大楼的桩柱及地基</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造大楼的楼房结构</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>建造贮油缸及液体燃料贮存设施</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>设计，供应及安装卷闸</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>楼房机电工程</li></ul><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>楼房装修工程</li></ul><br/>',18.00),(111,'tk7zrqgcp2ng0673m8uv1yjq','C&E Office, Queen\'s Warehouse and Agent\'s Offices','2025-06-02 06:59:36.913000','2025-07-07 07:13:55.672000',NULL,8,36,'en','C&E Office, Queen\'s Warehouse and Agent\'s Offices','River Trade Terminal Co. Ltd','01 March 1997 - 01 August 1998','<p>The major element of Works consisted of:</p><ul class=\"pl-6 list-disc [&amp;_ul]:list-[circle]\"><li>Construction of piles and foundation</li></ul><ul